      </h1>
      
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        See exactly where you're leaving money on the table. One dashboard that shows every affiliate's performance, identifies $1M+ in revenue opportunities, and tells you exactly what to fix.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="https://calendly.com/contact-mentyx/30min" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Schedule Demo
