                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="insight-content">
                <div class="insight-label">Opportunity</div>
                <div class="insight-text">Vegas Funding declining 35% more DSCR loans than group average. Consider training session.</div>
              </div>
              <button class="insight-action">Review Cases →</button>
            </div>

            <div class="insight-card insight-success">
              <div class="insight-icon">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="insight-content">
                <div class="insight-label">Best Practice</div>
                <div class="insight-text">Bluegrass Lending using <span class="ai-text">AI</span> pre-screening reduced decision time by 62%. Share across team?</div>
              </div>
              <button class="insight-action">Share Process →</button>
            </div>

            <div class="insight-card insight-alert">
              <div class="insight-icon">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                  <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
                  <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="insight-content">
                <div class="insight-label">Alert</div>
                <div class="insight-text">Low Tide Capital has 3 loans >75 days old. Risk of increased delinquency.</div>
              </div>
              <button class="insight-action">View Loans →</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Features Grid -->
<section class="features-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need to Manage Multiple Affiliates</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Built specifically for parent companies with lending affiliates</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/>
            <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/>
            <rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/>
            <rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Instant Affiliate Switching</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Toggle between affiliates in one click. See each entity's complete pipeline, performance metrics, and active loans while maintaining strict data isolation.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>One-click affiliate switching</li>
          <li>Individual affiliate dashboards</li>
          <li>Cross-affiliate comparison</li>
          <li>Automatic data isolation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
            <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Revenue Opportunity Alerts</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          AI automatically calculates how much revenue you're leaving on the table. See exactly what you'd earn if underperforming affiliates matched your top performers.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Automated revenue gap analysis</li>
          <li>Performance-based projections</li>
          <li>Specific improvement recommendations</li>
          <li>Monthly opportunity tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 20V10"/>
            <path d="M18 20V4"/>
            <path d="M6 20v-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Performance Benchmarking</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Compare affiliates side-by-side on approval rates, decision times, yield, and efficiency. Instantly identify top performers and who needs help.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Visual performance comparison</li>
          <li>Automated trend analysis</li>
          <li>Best practice identification</li>
          <li>Underperformer alerts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

